你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinancialConsulting.find_services', {'name': 'FinancialConsulting.find_services', 'description': 'This function searches for financial consulting services based on type and location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial consulting service, e.g., investment, retirement planning.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the service is provided.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'services', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching services, each with an ID, type, and provider.'}]}], ['FinancialConsulting.get_service_details', {'name': 'FinancialConsulting.get_service_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific financial consulting service given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'serviceId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the financial consulting service.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the service, including scope, fees, and terms.'}]}], ['FinancialConsulting.check_service_reviews', {'name': 'FinancialConsulting.check_service_reviews', 'description': 'This function checks reviews for multiple financial consulting services based on their IDs.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'serviceIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of service IDs to check reviews for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'reviews', 'description': 'A collection of reviews for the selected services.'}]}], ['FinancialConsulting.compare_services', {'name': 'FinancialConsulting.compare_services', 'description': 'This function compares multiple financial consulting services based on their IDs.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'serviceIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of service IDs to compare.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'comparison', 'description': 'A comparison of the selected services, highlighting differences in scope, fees, and terms.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinancialConsulting.find_services` 并传入 `type` 和 `location`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinancialConsulting.find_services",
    "args": "{'type': 'investment', 'location': 'California'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
